text: Hyloxalus excisus is a frog. It lives in Colombia. ==Home== Scientists have seen this frog in exactly one place: Quebrada La Ayura in Antioquia Department. They found it in a wet place with trees near a place where water comes up out of the ground. Scientists saw this frog 2200 meters above sea level. ==Danger== Scientists do not know if this frog is in danger of dying out. ==References== Category:Frogs of South America
title: Hyloxalus excisus
